room_title: Escape room "Sherlock's Secret" by Escape Port Charlotte in Fort Myers
room_address: 3191 Harbor Blvd Unit C Port Charlotte, FL 33952
room_description: The London Mafia has insider Intel that Sherlock Holmes houses the Star of Thames from a previous daring adventure, and in true thug fashion, they don’t plan on asking nicely for it. However, Sherlock isn’t home to protect the precious gem! Its your job to find out where Sherlock lives, get inside his apartment and make sure the Star does not end up in the hands of Londons most heinous criminals.
